description: A new recording purports to reveal how Russian state agents poisoned Putin critic Alexei Navalny.
title: Russian agent 'tricked into detailing Navalny assassination bid'
title_page: Russian agent 'tricked into detailing Navalny assassination bid' - BBC News
maintext: Mr Kudryavtsev told him the swift response of the airline pilot and the emergency medical team in Omsk, Siberia - where Mr Navalny was first treated - could have been the reason for the failure to kill him.
